The Springbok Rugby World Cup Squad. JOHANNESBURG - South Africa's 2019 Rugby World Cup squad was announced on Monday afternoon. Here they are: 1. Herschel Jantjies 2. Cobus Reinach 3. Warrick Gelant 4. Elton Jantjies 5. Handre Pollard 6. Makazole Mapimpi 7. Schalk Brits 8. Sbu Nkosi 9. Cheslin Kolbe 10. Faf de Klerk 11. Bongi Mbonambi 12. Malcolm Marx 13. Lukhanyo Am 14. Frans Malherbe 15. RG Snyman 16. Lood de Jager 17. Franco Mostert 18. Damian de Allende 19. Vincent Koch 20. Steven Kitshoff 21. Kwagga Smith 22. Trevor Nyakane 23. Willie le Roux 24. Frans Steyn 25. Francois Louw 26. Duane Vermeulen 27. Tendai Mtawarira 28. Eben Etzebeth 29. Pieter-Steph du Toit 30. Jesse Kriel 31. Siya Kolisi (Captain)